history.content:
Yeah you will be fine. I am currently taking CS 70 + EE 16B + Data X + 2 breaths. Just make sure to start everything ahead of time. EE16B is a lot of material and goes very fast (in a similar manner to CS 70). It might be very hard or not so hard depending on who teaches it. Be sure to be confident on what you learned in 54 + 16A and it'll not be that bad
